  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a RogueLike/Lite SpaceShooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is hard, with the complex movement system and spacial movement. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have to keep track of what item you wish to keep since you will only be able to hold 12 items at a time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, you will find your fair share of fun with great replayability after each run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*includes a save system</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                                                   With more than 100+ items</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/ba769d5644508cd2a4d902b0945c16f9.poster.avif?t=1731871169\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/ba769d5644508cd2a4d902b0945c16f9.webm?t=1731871169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/ba769d5644508cd2a4d902b0945c16f9.mp4?t=1731871169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                                                       Dozens of enemies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/0322e54c5d32bb130794a4f791a29bcf.poster.avif?t=1731871169\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/0322e54c5d32bb130794a4f791a29bcf.webm?t=1731871169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/0322e54c5d32bb130794a4f791a29bcf.mp4?t=1731871169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                                              You will have infinite possibilities</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/b4544afa7ec0af5f8d3cf5167c478daf.poster.avif?t=1731871169\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/b4544afa7ec0af5f8d3cf5167c478daf.webm?t=1731871169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/b4544afa7ec0af5f8d3cf5167c478daf.mp4?t=1731871169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a RogueLike/Lite SpaceShooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is hard, with the complex movement system and spacial movement. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have to keep track of what item you wish to keep since you will only be able to hold 12 items at a time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, you will find your fair share of fun with great replayability after each run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*includes a save system</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                                                   With more than 100+ items</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/ba769d5644508cd2a4d902b0945c16f9.poster.avif?t=1731871169\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/ba769d5644508cd2a4d902b0945c16f9.webm?t=1731871169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/ba769d5644508cd2a4d902b0945c16f9.mp4?t=1731871169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                                                       Dozens of enemies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/0322e54c5d32bb130794a4f791a29bcf.poster.avif?t=1731871169\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/0322e54c5d32bb130794a4f791a29bcf.webm?t=1731871169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/0322e54c5d32bb130794a4f791a29bcf.mp4?t=1731871169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                                              You will have infinite possibilities</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/b4544afa7ec0af5f8d3cf5167c478daf.poster.avif?t=1731871169\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/b4544afa7ec0af5f8d3cf5167c478daf.webm?t=1731871169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300370/extras/b4544afa7ec0af5f8d3cf5167c478daf.mp4?t=1731871169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
